Were you perma banned? No? Then it was clearly the warning. Every punishment is a warning except perma. And again, it is hate speech. Read the definition of hate speech carefully.

"Speech that attacks, threatens, or insults a person or group on the basis of national origin, ethnicity, color, religion, gender, gender identity, sexual orientation, or disability."

Now, if you're using this word that attacks someone, based on sexuality, is it not under this definition? You think about this one tonight, champ. I'm heading to bed.{{sticker:sg-ahri-2}}
